# 🅿️ Smart Park SaaS — Full Project Report
**Generated:** 2026-03-03 | **Status:** Running on localhost

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| **Frontend** | React 18 + TypeScript + Vite |
| **Styling** | TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui components |
| **Charts** | Recharts |
| **Maps** | Leaflet + react-leaflet |
| **Routing** | React Router v6 |
| **State/Data** | useState / useEffect (no global store) |
| **Backend** | Node.js + Express |
| **Database** | MySQL 8 (mysql2 driver) |
| **Auth** | JWT (jsonwebtoken, 8h expiry) |
| **Server Entry** | [server.js](file:///f:/parking/smart-park-saas/server.js) → port `5000` (via [.env](file:///f:/parking/smart-park-saas/.env)) |

---

## 🗄️ Database Schema

```
companies  ←──────────────────────────────────────┐
  id, name, latitude, longitude, created_at        │
                                                   │
users  ──────────────────────────────── tenant_id ─┤
  id, name, email, password,                       │
  role ENUM('super_admin','company_admin',          │
            'customer'),                           │
  tenant_id, company_name, created_at              │
                                                   │
slots  ─────────────────────────────── tenant_id ──┤
  id, tenant_id, slot_number, floor, type,         │
  status ENUM('available','occupied',               │
              'maintenance'),                      │
  price_per_hour                                   │
                                                   │
bookings  ──────────────── tenant_id, slot_id ─────┤
  id, tenant_id, user_id, slot_id,                 │
  vehicle_number, start_time, duration,            │
  end_time, status, total_amount, created_at       │
                                                   │
payments  ────────────── tenant_id, booking_id ────┘
  id, tenant_id, booking_id, amount,
  method, status ENUM('paid','pending','refunded'),
  created_at
```

---

## 🔑 Authentication & Role System

### Flow
```
User logs in → Backend verifies password → JWT issued
JWT contains: { user_id, role, tenant_id }
Frontend maps backend role → local role:
  "super_admin"   → "superadmin"
  "company_admin" → "admin"
  "customer"      → "user"
Session stored in localStorage (token, role, tenant_id, user_id, name, email)
```

### Demo Credentials
| Role | Email | Password |
|------|-------|----------|
| Super Admin | `super@demo.com` | `password` |
| Company Admin | `admin@demo.com` | `password` |
| Customer | `user@demo.com` | `password` |

---

## 👥 Role-Based Access

### 🔴 Super Admin (`super_admin`)
- Sees **all companies, all users, all payments** across every tenant
- Can **create** new parking companies via map click
- Can **edit** existing companies and their admins
- Can **delete** companies (cascades: slots, bookings, payments, users)
- Dashboard shows: total companies, total users, total completed bookings, total revenue

### 🟡 Company Admin (`company_admin`)
- Scoped to their **own tenant/company only**
- Manages **parking slots** (create, update status, delete)
- Views **all bookings** in their company
- Views **payments** for their company
- Dashboard shows: slot count, available slots, bookings, revenue

### 🟢 Customer (`customer`)
- Views **all company locations** on the map
- **Books parking slots** at any company
- Views **their own bookings** and history
- **Pays and exits** — triggers payment creation
- Views **their own payments**
- Can update their **profile**

---

## 🌐 API Endpoints

### Auth (`/api/auth`)
| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/auth/signup` | Register new user (customer/company_admin/super_admin) |
| POST | `/auth/login` | Login — returns JWT |

### User (`/api/user`) — requires auth, all roles
| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/user/locations` | All company locations with slot availability |
| GET | `/user/slots` | Slots (filtered by tenant for admins, all for customers) |
| GET | `/user/bookings` | Bookings (own for customers, tenant for admins) |
| POST | `/user/bookings` | Create a new booking |
| DELETE | `/user/bookings/:id` | Cancel a booking |
| POST | `/user/bookings/:id/exit` | Complete booking + calculate & record payment |
| GET | `/user/payments` | Payments (own for customers, tenant for admins) |
| GET | `/user/dashboard/stats` | Personal stats: total bookings, active, total spent |

### Admin (`/api/admin`) — requires `company_admin` or `super_admin`
| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/admin/slots` | All slots for current tenant |
| POST | `/admin/slots` | Create a new slot |
| PUT | `/admin/slots/:id` | Update slot status / number |
| DELETE | `/admin/slots/:id` | Delete a slot |
| GET | `/admin/dashboard/stats` | Tenant stats: slots, bookings, revenue |

### Super Admin (`/api/super`) — requires `super_admin`
| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/super/companies` | All companies (with admin info joined) |
| GET | `/super/companies/:id` | Company details + stats + recent payments |
| POST | `/super/companies` | Create company + assign admin (transaction) |
| PUT | `/super/companies/:id` | Update company + admin details |
| DELETE | `/super/companies/:id` | Delete company + all data (cascade transaction) |
| GET | `/super/users` | All users across all tenants |
| GET | `/super/payments` | All payments globally |

