## 🔧 Key Features Implemented

### ✅ Multi-Tenant Architecture
- Every table has `tenant_id` scoping data per company
- Admins only see their own company's data
- Super admin sees everything

### ✅ Live Parking Map
- Leaflet map showing all company locations as markers
- Super admin can **click the map** to open the "Create Company" modal (lat/lng auto-filled)
- User map shows available slots per location

### ✅ Booking + Exit Flow
- Customer selects company → selects available slot → enters vehicle number → creates booking
- On exit: duration calculated, amount = `ceil(hours) × price_per_hour`, payment recorded, slot freed

### ✅ Payment Gateway Simulation
- Multi-stage UI: "Connecting → Processing → Approved" with spinner/checkmark animations
- Supports Card, UPI, Cash methods

### ✅ Dark / Light Mode
- Full theme system using CSS variables
- Persisted across sessions

### ✅ Role-Aware Navigation
- Sidebar dynamically shows different links based on logged-in role
- No route guards on frontend (backend protects all sensitive endpoints with JWT)

