## 🐛 Bugs Fixed (This Session)

| # | Bug | Impact |
|---|-----|--------|
| 1 | `Users.tsx` filtered `role === 'user'` — DB uses `'customer'` | No users visible at all |
| 2 | `Users.tsx` used `company_id` — API returns `tenant_id` | Company column always "None" |
| 3 | `DashboardSuperAdmin` Save button was a toast stub | Companies couldn't be created/edited |
| 4 | `DashboardSuperAdmin` Delete button was a toast stub | Companies couldn't be deleted |
| 5 | Revenue chart used `Math.random()` | Chart showed garbage data on every render |
| 6 | Stats showed hardcoded `1420 / $32,800` | Stats were always wrong |
| 7 | `loadData` only fetched companies + users | Missing payments for stats |
| 8 | `console.error` on load failure | Silent failures, no user feedback |
| 9 | `apiUpdateCompany` + `apiDeleteCompany` didn't exist in `api.ts` | TypeScript would fail to compile |
| 10 | Unused imports (`LineChart`, `Line`, `MapPin`) | Dead code / minor lint noise |

